import React from "react"
import { BrowserRouter, Route, Switch } from "react-router-dom"
import Main from "../src/pages/Main/Main"

const Routes = () =>(
    <BrowserRouter>
        <Switch>
            <Route exact path = "/" component = {() => <Main/>} />
            
        </Switch>
    </BrowserRouter>
)

export default Routes;
